var finalList = ["Thank you for shopping with us !", "I hope this beverage treats you well ! ", "There are many beverages that can help you acquire a healthy diet !", "Enjoy !", "Thank You !"];
var total = 0;
var weightLoss = 0;
var weightGain = 0;
var milkshake = 0;
var index = 0;

//onEvent for recommendation button
// takes user to screen with recommendations 
//based of user selction
onEvent("Recommendation", "click", function( ) {
  setScreen("screen2");
// The images used in this screen came from:
// [1] image 1 - https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/img-2984-1544045336.jpg
// [2] image 2 - https://images.cookforyourlife.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/shutterstock_406826704.jpg
// [3] image 3 - https://yogaofcooking.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/oreo-milkshake-4-1040x1536.jpg
// The information found in the first paragraph came from
//https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/are-smoothies-good-for-you
//The information found in the second paragraph came from
//https://theinfinitekitchen.com/guide/what-smoothies-are-good-for-weight-gain/
});

//onEvent for "buy some now" button
// takes user to screen with selections 
//user can buy smoothies with calculated total
onEvent("buy", "click", function( ) {
setScreen("screen3");
});

//onEvent for restart button
// takes user to home screen  
onEvent("restart", "click", function( ) {
setScreen("home");
restart();
});

//onEvent for restart button
// resets all numbers on the screen   
onEvent("image1", "click", function( ) {
restart();
});

//onEvent for weight loss selection
// increases amount of weight loss smoothies
onEvent("loss", "click", function( ) {
 losses();
});

//onEvent for weight gain selection
//increases amount of weight gain smoothies
onEvent("gain", "click", function( ) {
  Gains();
});

//onEvent for milkshake selection
// increases amount of milkshakes
onEvent("milkshake", "click", function( ) {
  tasty();
});

// function to add up total for weightloss smoothies
// weightloss - increases smoothie numbers wanted
// return losses - returns amount selected 
function losses() {
   weightLoss = weightLoss + 1;
  setProperty("Ls", "text", "" + weightLoss); 
  return losses;
}

// function to add up total for weightGain smoothies
// weightGain - increases smoothie numbers wanted
// return Gains - returns amount selected 
function Gains() {
    weightGain = weightGain + 1;
  setProperty("Gs", "text", "" + weightGain);
  return Gains;
}

// function to add up total for milkshake
// milkshake - increases smoothie numbers wanted
// return tasty - returns amount selected 
function tasty() {
   milkshake = milkshake + 1;
  setProperty("Ts", "text", "" + milkshake);
  return tasty;
}

// function restarts all numbers 
// restart just restarts everything in the app
// return tasty - returnes all the values the original 
function restart() {
total = 0;
weightLoss = 0;
weightGain = 0;
milkshake = 0;
setNumber("Ls", 0);
setNumber("Gs", 0);
setNumber("Ts", 0);
setText("totalText", "$0");
setText("kind","Kind of Smoothie..." );
setText("reason","Health Purpose...");

}

//onEvent for total button
// calculates users final price after smoothie selection 
//user enters the amount -  total is returned
onEvent("total", "click", function( ) {
  totalCalc();
  final();
});

// function is for calculating price
// total - adds the amount of smoothies * price
// return totalcalc - returns the total cost
function totalCalc() {
  var price = 4.99;
for (var i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
 if (weightGain > 0 || weightLoss > 0 || milkshake > 0) {
   total = weightGain * price + weightLoss * price + milkshake * price;
 }
  }
  setText("totalText", "$" + total);
  return totalCalc;
}
function final() {
  index = randomNumber(0, finalList.length - 1);
  setText("final", finalList[index]);
}
